Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:04.41,Base,,0,0,0,,Everyday here is just "basics, basics, basics."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:08.80,Base,,0,0,0,,That's all we've done since we started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.04,Base,,0,0,0,,And the Phantom's class is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:13.04,Base,,0,0,0,,We could ask for something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Mr. Andou!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:37.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Everyone dreams of becoming a superstar at least once
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:42.77,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So that you can make the world envious
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:45.52,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}1, 2, 3, quick like Allegro
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Hold that hand and come
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:52.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Let's build a rainbow together at Andante
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:58.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}You aren't anyone yet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:03.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So any of your future can come true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:09.72,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Your dream is just beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:14.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Little by little, you can become yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:20.31,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Tomorrow's gonna blow another wind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:24.23,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}So dream as many times as you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:29.71,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Someday, become the stage's sparkling star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:34.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}so that the spotlight shines upon you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:50.44,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(1575,801)}"A Glimpse of Stardom"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:53.12,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Today, we'll be talking about the\NStanislavski technique and how to—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:58.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Why do you all look dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Andou! Can I make a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.08,Base,,0,0,0,,She's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.33,Base,,0,0,0,,She's actually asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.58,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you girls plotting?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Shoot, Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:10.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:16.37,Base,,0,0,0,,So, there's one crucial skill that\Nevery other teacher has mentioned to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 454)}Expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:21.09,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 491)}Expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:23.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:27.97,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew who every teacher was\Nwithout her even saying their names.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:28.97,Base,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:34.97,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And {\i0}I believe the class where we'll learn {\i1}how {\i0}to express ourselves the most is this acting class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.74,Base,,0,0,0,,We've been Kouka students for four months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:41.53,Base,,0,0,0,,So we think it might be nice if we, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.48,Base,,0,0,0,,had a little opportunity to actually {\i1}act{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.92,Base,,0,0,0,,Is that your suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:57.75,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, I've been here eight years, and the\Nacting curriculum has never changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:03:02.89,Base,,0,0,0,,First-year students are expected to sit\Npolitely and learn the basics of acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:06.01,Base,,0,0,0,,That's how it's been done at\Nthe Kouka School for a century now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.47,Base,,0,0,0,,But here's an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe, do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:14.94,Base,,0,0,0,,Show me what I sound like when I say "expression."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:17.64,Base,,0,0,0,,If I think it's good, I'll consider your suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.65,Base,,0,0,0,,Those are high stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:24.90,Base,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of pressure, but here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.28,Base,,0,0,0,,"Expression"? Can you eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.27,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, open your textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.87,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So much for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry I couldn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:43.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Actually, Sara—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:48.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe, that was a good impression of Mr. Andou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.60,Base,,0,0,0,,It so was!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:52.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was {\i1}too {\i0}good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.02,Base,,0,0,0,,There's a package here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.78,Base,,0,0,0,,13, 14, 15, 16 roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.53,Base,,0,0,0,,Sara— Watanabe, is today...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:12.03,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep! I turn 16 years old today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:13.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Today's your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.58,Base,,0,0,0,,Aww, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:25.04,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My first friend's birthday is today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:28.38,Base,,0,0,0,,So who gave you this bouquet of roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:30.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Is it a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Ohmigosh, your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Maybe! He lives in Tokyo,\Nso we're long-distance right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.51,Base,,0,0,0,,but it could be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.32,Base,,0,0,0,,A-And he's a real, live person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.35,Base,,0,0,0,,Not some anime guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:48.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Is that the person you're always messaging?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:55.16,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Happy Birthday"\N"from your fan of the red rose"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.16,Base,,0,0,0,,What the hell? That's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:59.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Sara— Watanabe, does your boyfriend\Nlike these sorts of gestures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.63,Base,,0,0,0,,That's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.15,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kouzaburou"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.67,Base,,0,0,0,,You sure are in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:13.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I be?\NIt's Sarasa's 16th birthday, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.06,Base,,0,0,0,,You knew that, right, Akiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.40,Base,,0,0,0,,Of course I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:20.05,Base,,0,0,0,,So, did you send her any present?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.81,Base,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are {\i0}her boyfriend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.44,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna give it to her\Nwhen she comes home this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:33.74,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, where's your passion?\NI sent her a bouquet of 16 roses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.79,Base,,0,0,0,,She's so incredibly special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:40.00,Base,,0,0,0,,And this is her special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Wait... hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:46.13,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I didn't say it was from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:49.77,Base,,0,0,0,,I said it was from her "fan of the red rose."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:52.01,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Happy Birthday"\N"from your fan of the red rose"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:52.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Her fan of the red rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:57.26,Base,,0,0,0,,Forget summer vacation. \NWhy not just send her something now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.53,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll send her a text message tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:04.02,Base,,0,0,0,,You gonna stop by her grandpa's place tonight again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.52,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(960,441.667)}"Happy Birthday, Sarasa! I'll give you\Nyour present over summer break!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:16.01,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her boyfriend's a frog? And a bot at that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.82,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why does a bot have a private account?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.08,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let that frog outdo me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:28.01,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna give Watanabe something\Nshe'll love even more than those roses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:31.56,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, she's the first friend I ever made.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:37.14,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now's the perfect chance\Nto call her by her given name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.09,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I jump straight to nicknames?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.10,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sara? Or Sasa?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.98,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or just plain Sarasa?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:46.99,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, geez!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:57.24,Base,,0,0,0,,The hardest-to-get lottery prize figurine\Nof Tsukahara Vault Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:59.61,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, Great Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:05.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai, you got this for me, didn't you? I could cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:09.22,Base,,0,0,0,,I tried four times to win it and only won hand towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.68,0:07:10.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Well, Sara—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe, you're always going on and on about {\i1}Floor Kings{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.51,Base,,0,0,0,,so I gave it a go and won the top prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.38,Base,,0,0,0,,In one try?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.89,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, more than ten or twenty times.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.35,Base,,0,0,0,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.14,Base,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.02,Base,,0,0,0,,Especially this part!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.03,Base,,0,0,0,,"To {\i1}Sarasa{\i0}. Sorry it's late.\NHappy birthday."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't read it out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.00,Base,,0,0,0,,You used my given name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.15,Base,,0,0,0,,"To {\i1}Sarasa{\i0}"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:35.70,Base,,0,0,0,,Look, Sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:43.12,Base,,0,0,0,,Just call me Sarasa!\NWe're friends, aren't we, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Sarasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:53.19,Base,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0, 350)}Oh, my Taku! Ai called me "Sarasa"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.63,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm super happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:57.92,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.55,Base,,0,0,0,,About your practicals on acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.66,Base,,0,0,0,,I got the permission on the staff meeting yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.81,Base,,0,0,0,,Quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:09.31,Base,,0,0,0,,We're going to perform a scene from\NShakespeare's {\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.06,Base,,0,0,0,,The roles are Romeo, Juliet,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:16.82,Base,,0,0,0,,Tybalt, and Juliet's Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:21.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Each group of four will have two weeks\Nto prepare their scene on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:21.90,Base,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:23.17,Base,,0,0,0,,On our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Mr. Andou, what do you mean by "on our own"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Is this not a class activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:29.46,Base,,0,0,0,,We got duped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.91,Base,,0,0,0,,He's just slacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:35.84,Base,,0,0,0,,Now, now, I {\i1}did {\i0}have to fight a bit in that staff meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:40.18,Base,,0,0,0,,They let us do this under the assumption\Nthat this would be an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:44.74,Base,,0,0,0,,So I haven't prepared any materials\Nor plans for guiding you to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:48.69,Base,,0,0,0,,You'll rehearse on your own,\Nthen in two weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:52.62,Base,,0,0,0,,we'll spend one class period\Npresenting our scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:56.61,Base,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll give you {\i1}thorough{\i0}\Nfeedback on your performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.16,Base,,0,0,0,,Also, since this was your idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.86,Base,,0,0,0,,you won't complain if we end up\Nusing it for next year's practicals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.41,Base,,0,0,0,,Crafty bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.11,Base,,0,0,0,,Of course, we don't have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.64,Base,,0,0,0,,We'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.93,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We drew lots to make five groups, each of 4 students.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:16.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Group E.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.88,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(1410.667,404.333)}"Group E"\N"Sarasa Watanabe"\N"Hoshino Kaoru"\N"Chika Sawada"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Guess we're with you, Sarasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:24.09,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep! Let's break a leg, Group E!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.59,Base,,0,0,0,,How do we wanna pick roles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:31.37,Base,,0,0,0,,Sarasa and I both want to be Male Lead,\Nso we'll pick between Romeo and Tybalt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.78,Base,,0,0,0,,Rock-paper-scissors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:33.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:37.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Then Narata and I will play Female Leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Want to do rock-paper-scissors, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.03,Base,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.73,Base,,0,0,0,,Sweet! I'll take Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.37,Base,,0,0,0,,That means I'm Tybalt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.29,Base,,0,0,0,,What about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:50.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!\NRock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:58.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Um, I'll play, uh, Ju...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Juliet's Nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.19,0:10:02.32,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, I wanted to play that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:05.17,Base,,0,0,0,,A comic role will be the perfect challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:07.87,Base,,0,0,0,,You'll make a better Juliet than me, anyway, Narata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:11.45,Base,,0,0,0,,Really? I can play Juliet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.60,Base,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.16,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,We've always {\i1}loved{\i0} Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.07,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.48,Base,,0,0,0,,I wanted to play the Nurse, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.24,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then Narata's our Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:22.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:28.36,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tatami Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.74,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's start with a quick readthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:34.50,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest, I think Sarasa would be better off as Romeo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.37,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}instead of the darker Tybalt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.42,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially after that evening when\Nwe were walking back from the theater,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:45.44,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she recited those few mesmerizing lines as Romeo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, you start, Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:48.93,Base,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:56.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Madam, your mother craves a word with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:59.28,Base,,0,0,0,,Good woman! Who is her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:04.44,Base,,0,0,0,,Why sir, her mother is the lady of the house, Lady Capulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:07.95,Base,,0,0,0,,Is she a Capulet? O dear account!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.00,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's up next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.66,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Show me the passion that's\Ndriving you to become a top star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.45,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Show us all you've got!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:20.11,Base,,0,0,0,,That voice, is that Romeo?\NRomeo, of house Montague?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:27.80,Base,,0,0,0,,How dare the man come hither,\Nto the Cap... Capulet Mansion itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.52,Base,,0,0,0,,How are you this bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.64,Base,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around and get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.19,Base,,0,0,0,,I-I wasn't messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:38.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Whatever! We don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.99,Base,,0,0,0,,Juliet, your lines are next!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:50.99,Base,,0,0,0,,See? Your crappy reading threw Narata off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.03,Base,,0,0,0,,My, what are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.46,Base,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:59.00,Base,,0,0,0,,What's this about? Some secret meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:03.97,Base,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! Mr. Andou filled us\Nall in on your little scene exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.25,Base,,0,0,0,,You first-years are already getting to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:09.57,Base,,0,0,0,,Boy, you girls are lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:13.01,Base,,0,0,0,,And you're doing {\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}? That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:18.08,Base,,0,0,0,,One thing, though: you really can't\Nuse this room to practice, mmkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.76,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"First-Year Lockers"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Hijiri was really mad at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.70,Base,,0,0,0,,She was? But she was all smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.53,Base,,0,0,0,,That's how you can tell when she's angry—she's {\i1}smiling{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.53,Base,,0,0,0,,Ugh, we can't use the tatami room anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Where should we practice from now on, then, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:38.30,Base,,0,0,0,,Group A's using the lecture hall,\Nbut they might let us share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:42.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we use half the lecture hall with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.24,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't see why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.04,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:44.71,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:46.11,Base,,0,0,0,,W-We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.30,Base,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:51.80,Base,,0,0,0,,W-We're doing the same scene,\Nso we'll throw each other off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.60,Base,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna share a place\Nto practice with another group!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:13:00.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Then where do we practice?\NAll the other rooms are already taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Why don't we just do it out on the sidewalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:03.89,Base,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:06.65,Base,,0,0,0,,The sidewalk? Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:11.15,Base,,0,0,0,,We are students of the 100th class\Nof the {\i1}esteemed {\i0}Kouka School!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:16.16,Base,,0,0,0,,We can't perform on the sidewalk!\NWhat a way to ruin Kouka for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:20.79,Base,,0,0,0,,We might be students now, \Nbut we are destined to be professionals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:22.87,Base,,0,0,0,,Take it seriously, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:28.58,Base,,0,0,0,,I have to use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:32.83,Base,,0,0,0,,That scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.14,Base,,0,0,0,,Who pissed her off?\N You {\i1}know{\i0} she's got a really short fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.04,Base,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:43.42,Base,,0,0,0,,Her mom was a Kouka actress,\Nand her grandma was a top Female Lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.88,Base,,0,0,0,,It's the pressure that puts on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Hoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:56.20,Base,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being a loudmouth with a short fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:00.28,Base,,0,0,0,,There was a girl like you in JPX.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.70,Base,,0,0,0,,She was our group leader and was always angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:06.38,Base,,0,0,0,,What, you come to rub it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:11.21,Base,,0,0,0,,I never went to high school, and barely\Nwent to elementary and middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:16.34,Base,,0,0,0,,So Sarasa wasn't the reason I couldn't\Nread Juliet's lines this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.84,Base,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.26,Base,,0,0,0,,...can't read kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:28.95,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Favorite Place: beech"\N"Why: Its suthing"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:28.59,Base,,0,0,0,,Back in JPX, I was used to my manager\Nwriting the readings down for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:33.48,Base,,0,0,0,,This morning was the first time\NI realized how screwed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.29,Base,,0,0,0,,None of us have any experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:40.50,Base,,0,0,0,,so unless you get mad at us,\Nwe'll just end up holding you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.72,0:14:43.46,Base,,0,0,0,,What the hell? That's so not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.08,Base,,0,0,0,,What if I don't want to be the bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.53,Base,,0,0,0,,Then Group E fails together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.90,Base,,0,0,0,,Is that a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.93,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Nono Park"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:57.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah! How is this park?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.37,Base,,0,0,0,,It's not the sidewalk, that's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:02.89,Base,,0,0,0,,Chika and I looked all over\Nfor a good spot to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Will this work, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.82,Base,,0,0,0,,Not like we can go anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:12.01,Base,,0,0,0,,Not that this two weeks of prep is gonna affect our grades, but let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.81,Base,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Group E!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.21,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.06,Base,,0,0,0,,Really, Sugimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.45,Base,,0,0,0,,You're gonna lend me your Blu-ray of\NWinter Troupe {\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:23.49,Base,,0,0,0,,Kaoru asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.63,Base,,0,0,0,,She said if you don't level up, and fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:30.31,Base,,0,0,0,,then "Group E's gonna drag\Nthe rest of our class down with them."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:33.67,Base,,0,0,0,,That Hoshino doesn't mince words, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:40.43,Base,,0,0,0,,Sugimoto lent me her copy of \N{\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}, wanna watch it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:44.11,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Kanji Dictionary"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:44.11,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm good. I wanna finish the Kanji writings before I sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:48.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay! Could I borrow your Blu-ray player and headphones?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:54.42,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna study so hard,\N I'm gonna knock the socks off Hoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.91,Base,,0,0,0,,Let's do an awesome job tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:58.79,Base,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:04.86,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder where the Sarasa\Nwe saw that day disappeared to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.03,Base,,0,0,0,,That voice, is that Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.51,Base,,0,0,0,,Romeo, of house Montague?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:16.29,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,How dare the man come hither,\Nto the Capulet Mansion itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:18.97,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Such sins shall not be endured!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.50,Base,,0,0,0,,Such sins shall not be endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.93,Base,,0,0,0,,So, how's your Group E looking, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.88,Base,,0,0,0,,Especially, how's Sarasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.61,Base,,0,0,0,,I kinda don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Like, it's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.64,Base,,0,0,0,,Creepy how?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:38.06,Base,,0,0,0,,You know how you're supposed to improve little by little?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.30,Base,,0,0,0,,Sarasa just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.26,Base,,0,0,0,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:53.35,Base,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Mr. Andou doesn't expect us to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:57.52,Base,,0,0,0,,Then why did the Phantom even want us to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.73,0:17:03.70,Base,,0,0,0,,Probably because he wanted to see how much fun we'd have, or how much effort we'd put into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:04.67,Base,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:08.60,Base,,0,0,0,,I mean, isn't playing pretend \Nway more fun when you've got friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.72,Base,,0,0,0,,We only had two weeks to put this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:18.43,Base,,0,0,0,,But when I get to play Lady Oscar, I'll remember these last two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:21.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Enough about Oscar. That {\i1}was {\i0}fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.35,Base,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.63,Base,,0,0,0,,Just keep going until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:29.33,Base,,0,0,0,,But give it your all, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.70,Base,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's give it our all to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.85,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, each group gets 15 minutes to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.70,Base,,0,0,0,,I've marked out the 'stage' with tape,\Nso use that as a guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.61,Base,,0,0,0,,Group A is first...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:44.17,Base,,0,0,0,,...most of the time, so let's go with Group E.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.54,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to go {\i0}first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:49.85,Base,,0,0,0,,We didn't even think about the size of the actual stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:51.86,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's imagine it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.68,Base,,0,0,0,,There's a balcony up above,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.68,Base,,0,0,0,,and a big ballroom in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.86,Base,,0,0,0,,The lights are tinged with blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.75,Base,,0,0,0,,and there's a crescent moon through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.38,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,What beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:10.28,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,631)}She shines like a rich jewel amidst the crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:13.68,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Love! This, truly, is love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:17.84,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,My life's road has led me to her beautiful flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:17.84,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'mon, now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.35,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop trying to gauge my reaction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.96,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep looking at me, and you'll flub your lines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:26.10,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Good woman! Who is her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:31.80,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Why sir, her mother is the lady of the house, Lady Capulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:31.80,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She sure is spry for an old lady.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:35.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Her daughter is a visage of beauty, and intelligent, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:39.16,Base,,0,0,0,,How fortunate I am to have nursed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:42.95,Base,,0,0,0,,She is a visage of beauty, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.04,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I messed up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.63,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, no, I'm gonna cry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.56,Flashback,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if we mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.43,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Just keep going until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.76,Base,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:19:00.26,Base,,0,0,0,,I felt those qualities of such importance, I said them twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.58,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice save.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:06.82,Base,,0,0,0,,My! Come hither, nurse!\NWhere goeth yonder gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:09.29,Base,,0,0,0,,The man with visage radiant as the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:13.78,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can tell she's had experience\Nbeing on a big stage before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.55,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,There, him now who is going out of door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.55,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But boy, this Juliet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.05,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is {\i0}so {\i1}not in love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:23.31,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,Go ask his name, if he be married...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:23.31,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, she keeps looking at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.31,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But not like Hoshino did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:30.29,Base - Top,,0,0,0,,My only love, sprung from my only hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.29,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on, Narata...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.32,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you performing for an audience of {\i0}one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:37.53,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, next up, our Kouka misfit, Watanabe Sarasa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.53,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Group E Roles"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.15,Base,,0,0,0,,That voice, is that Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.18,Base,,0,0,0,,Romeo, of house Montague?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:49.78,Base,,0,0,0,,How dare the man come hither,\Nto the Capulet mansion itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.06,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's directing her gaze at the balcony seats.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.16,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And she's keeping her eyes at a 45-degree\Nangle so the lights will catch them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:56.05,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impressive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.55,Base,,0,0,0,,Fetch me my rapier, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.19,Base,,0,0,0,,That Romeo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.09,Base,,0,0,0,,...is naught but a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:11.57,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watanabe Sarasa was reborn overnight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:15.63,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And because today, she has an audience,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.95,Base,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's even more—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:20.10,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay! Good job, Group E.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:24.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Here's a question for you.\NWho did you imagine as your audience?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.60,Base,,0,0,0,,The people in this room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.87,Base,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.39,Base,,0,0,0,,A full house with balcony seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.56,0:20:32.45,Base,,0,0,0,,One person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:35.65,Base,,0,0,0,,So that's why you were\Nstaring at me that whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:36.38,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.43,Base,,0,0,0,,In JPX, they told us that even if\Nwe only had an audience of one,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:44.89,Base,,0,0,0,,we should direct our performance\Ntowards them and give it our all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.87,Base,,0,0,0,,That's a good thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:53.15,Base,,0,0,0,,but the Kouka theater holds 2,500 people,\Nand every performance is a full house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:58.49,Base,,0,0,0,,When you're acting, you should act\Nfor every one of those 2,500 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.15,Base,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:03.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Also, Narata, if you're going to play\Na Female Lead, try to be a little sweeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:06.26,Base,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen\Na Juliet who didn't smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.25,Base,,0,0,0,,Next, Sawada Chika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:08.98,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:12.48,Base,,0,0,0,,Great recovery after you flubbed your line there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:17.47,Base,,0,0,0,,But just hunching over doesn't make you an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.34,Base,,0,0,0,,Use that imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:20.19,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:21.83,Base,,0,0,0,,Next up, Hoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:22.60,Base,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:25.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't let your mind stray when you're performing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.56,Base,,0,0,0,,Leave yourself behind when you step on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:28.39,Base,,0,0,0,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:30.29,Base,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:32.00,Base,,0,0,0,,For now, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:35.20,Base,,0,0,0,,You haven't learned any skills yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.32,Base,,0,0,0,,so I want you to act\Nhowever you want for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:42.23,Base,,0,0,0,,Don't get too hung up on my critique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.66,Base,,0,0,0,,Right, last up, Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:45.33,Base,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:48.62,Base,,0,0,0,,Your impression was uncanny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.90,0:21:50.96,Base,,0,0,0,,I'll admit, I was shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.99,Base,,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry, Watanabe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:57.10,Base,,0,0,0,,you'll never be a top star.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:04.15,Base,,0,0,0,,If you don't change, you'll never be\Na top star of the Kouka Opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:29.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I'll keep walking on the path that glows white in the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.86,0:22:35.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}A long, narrow path that can only be walked alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.86,0:22:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I walk forward so that I won't fall behind other people's shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:49.53,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If I just head straight forward, it'll appear right in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:52.82,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Now, let's open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.69,0:22:57.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}There are sparkling stars in this vast sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.44,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}If just I had wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.06,0:23:07.02,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}I'd flap and flutter high through the space like a bird
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:13.70,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}Going around the constellations, and pursuing the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:20.17,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur9}we had just started this endless journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:39.98,Base,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Act 7: The Hanamichi\Nand the Silver Bridge"
